# Terraform-init
This directory contains the code to create the terraform backend resources S3 and dynamodb. We need to run this terraform module one time to create the resources.

This module requires the following varaibles to run.

state_bucket

lock_table

region

## Commands to run and execute

### Init Terraform resources

```
terraform init && \
(terraform import aws_s3_bucket.terraform_state "starcap-devops-tf-state" 2>/dev/null || true) && \
(terraform import aws_dynamodb_table.terraform_locks "starcap-devops-tf-state-lock" 2>/dev/null || true)
```
### Validate Terraform resources

```
terraform validate
```

### Plan Terraform resources

```
terraform plan -out plan.out
```

### Apply Terraform resources

```
terraform apply -auto-approve plan.out
```
